<p>Bulma tags are used in a few different layouts in Bulma Clean Theme, so it has been extracted as itâ€™s own component. You can create a tag in your own pages using the below include tag.</p>

<p><span class="tag  is-success ">
    An example tag
</span></p>

<h2 id="tag-include">Tag Include</h2>

<p>To include a tag use the following include.</p>

<p><code>
{% include tag.html tag="The tag text" %}
</code></p>

<p>You can overwrite the default style (is-primary) by passing in the style in the include tag.</p>

<p><code>
{% include tag.html tag="The tag text" style="is-light" %}
</code></p>
